# Demo Success Criteria

The demo is successful if it clearly shows:

1. User authentication
2. Trip creation
3. Structured itinerary planning
4. Invitation workflow
5. Shared trip membership
6. Post-trip rating
7. Template publishing
8. Template cloning

---

# Presentation Emphasis

## Product Value to emphasize
- collaborative planning
- structured day-by-day organization
- reusable trip knowledge through templates
- post-trip feedback through ratings

## UX Value to emphasize
- easy to start
- clear organization
- visually easy to understand
- suitable for real travel scenarios

